reviewText: I highly recommend this DVD even if you don't speak Spanish.

Bought this video for my little niece for when we go on long trips.
She absolutely loves it. It keeps her busy.

I can't say enough good things about this video. It is perfect for babies and toddlers because they are short music videos that keep the baby entertained, rather than 30-minute episodes or movies, which are too long for a baby or toddler. My daughter loves these. Wish they were easier to get a hold of so I could give them to everybody.
My two year old LOVES this set of videos...and it takes me back to my childhood! Well made and great sound!
Excellents videos all in 3D. Background of Argentine culture and music. Mi son love it,I higly recomend this DVD you can also do karaoke
